    title: 'Cofounder',
    org: 'Anonymonkey LLC · Chicago, IL',
    body: "Booth's Polsky Accelerator, $15K seed funding, 2nd place New Venture Challenge. Led development of an app to automate management of anonymous communities on Facebook, scaling to 10,000+ daily active users and 6M+ daily impressions. Built a global ambassador program across 16 countries and five languages.",
    skills: ['research'],
